  "texts": [
    "Following standard practices, we fine-tuned these GLMs by feeding completed prompts into the model.",
    "Each prompt consisted of (1) a set of scoring instructions, and (2) a student response.",
    "These prompts were completed by adding (3) the \"true score\" of response to the end of each prompt.",
    "Exact wording of the prompt templates are included below.",
    "We did not attempt any prompt-tuning, i.e., optimizing the (wording of the) prompt itself or using in-context learning (i.e. few-shot learning)."
  ],
